  "description": "Welcome home to this charming Seattle gem - perfect for first-time homebuyers looking to put down roots in one of the city's most desirable neighborhoods. This beautifully maintained 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers 1,800 square feet of thoughtfully designed living space that seamlessly blends modern updates with classic character.

Step inside to discover gleaming hardwood floors throughout, leading you to a stunning updated kitchen that's sure to inspire your inner chef. The open-concept layout creates an ideal space for both everyday living and entertaining, while large windows flood the home with natural light.

All three bedrooms provide generous proportions, with the primary bedroom offering ample closet space and en-suite bathroom access. The second full bathroom has been tastefully updated with modern fixtures and finishes.

One of this home's standout features is the expansive backyard - a private oasis perfect for summer barbecues, gardening enthusiasts, or creating your own outdoor retreat. The well-maintained landscape offers plenty of room for pets, play areas, or future additions.

Located in a friendly, established neighborhood, you'll enjoy easy access to Seattle's best amenities, including local parks, shopping, dining, and major commute routes.",
